{"data": [{"id": "4742563", "title": "ECB Preview: Gut Feeling Vs. Model-Based Judgement", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"European Union flag in front of the Eurotower in Frankfurt\" data-id=\"184866840\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">instamatics</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/carsten-brzeski/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Carsten Brzeski</a></em></p> <p>Somehow, we are back at where we were ahead of the European Central Bank's October meeting. The only difference this time around is not whether to cut or halt, but rather whether to cut by 25bp or by 50bp. As</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/184866840/image_184866840.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742563-ecb-preview-gut-feeling-vs-model-based-judgement", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 12:25:00"}, {"id": "4742549", "title": "Salesforce: Q4 Guidance Signals Continued Deceleration In Revenue Growth", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Salesforce logo at its Corporate office in New York, NY, USA on August 18, 2022.\" data-id=\"1445233045\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>What Happened</h2> <p>Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>) rallied more than 10% despite missing its non-GAAP EPS consensus and guiding a lower YoY revenue growth in 4Q FY2025. While management's discussion on its featured Agentforce platform was promising, it did not seem to justify this</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445233045/image_1445233045.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742549-salesforce-stock-q4-guidance-signals-continued-deceleration-revenue-growth-reiterate-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 12:04:53"}, {"id": "4742554", "title": "Korn Ferry 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Korn Ferry in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106058\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742554-korn-ferry-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:39:47"}, {"id": "4742541", "title": "SentinelOne: Scaling Faster And Creating Value", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Female climber on a rocky wall\" data-id=\"1189534859\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"921px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Buena Vista Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I have analyzed the cybersecurity sector via several ETFs such as <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733562-bug-dont-bug-me-rating-downgrade\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4733562-bug-dont-bug-me-rating-downgrade\" target=\"_blank\">Global X Cybersecurity</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BUG\" title=\"Global X Funds - Global X Cybersecurity ETF\">BUG</a>) and the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4677154-cibr-underperforming-the-cybersecurity-sector\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4677154-cibr-underperforming-the-cybersecurity-sector\" target=\"_blank\">First Trust NASDAQ Cybersecurity</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CIBR\" title=\"First Trust Nasdaq CEA Cybersecurity ETF\">CIBR</a>), which did not instill me with enthusiasm or conviction</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1189534859/image_1189534859.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742541-sentinelone-stock-scaling-faster-creating-value", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:33:45"}, {"id": "4742539", "title": "China Yuchai International: Significant R&D Focus And Rising Exposure To ESG Trend, Yet Undervalued", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Closeup of team members examine ESG-related documents, pointing and discussing investment strategies for sustainable and renewable energy resources. Eco-Friendly Business Discussing ESG Goals.\" data-id=\"2148427753\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">MTStock Studio/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>China Yuchai International Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CYD\" title=\"China Yuchai International Limited\">CYD</a></span>) is making large investments in research &amp; development and offering innovations like the 350hp IE-Power Hybrid system. In addition, the company appears to have beneficial relationships with the public sector. The Government of Nanning</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148427753/image_2148427753.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742539-china-yuchai-international-significant-r-and-d-focus-rising-exposure-esg-trend-yet-undervalued", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:29:30"}, {"id": "4742537", "title": "Ramaco's Latest Announcement Makes It Worse For Me, Not Better", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"fiery grill\" data-id=\"187048012\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bjones27/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Ramaco's Economics Just Look Wrong</h2> <p>Ramaco Resources (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/METC\" title=\"Ramaco Resources, Inc.\">METC</a></span>) has just released a press piece stating that the rare earth mine is even more exciting than we'd at first been told. For there is the metallurgical coal - which, as</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/187048012/image_187048012.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742537-ramaco-resources-latest-announcement-makes-it-worse-for-me-not-better", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:23:57"}, {"id": "4742536", "title": "Salesforce Q3 Review: Growth Is Still Slowing", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Salesforce Tower San Francisco Downtown\" data-id=\"1025006372\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JasonDoiy</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>Co-Authored by Noah Cox and Brock Heilig</em></p> <h2>Investment Thesis</h2> <p>While Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>) shares are up roughly 34.61% since the last time I wrote on the software maker, I continue to be bearish on the technology giant on the back</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1025006372/image_1025006372.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742536-salesforce-stock-q3-review-growth-still-slowing-reiterate-strong-sell", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:14:10"}, {"id": "4742535", "title": "Bayer's Stock Hits 2-Decade Low: Why It Is A Buy Again", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Sign BAYER on buildings of chemical industry in Leverkusen\" data-id=\"1843440175\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"948px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Fotofantastika</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Bayer AG's (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAYRY\" title=\"Bayer Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:BAYRY</a>), (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BAYZF\" title=\"Bayer Aktiengesellschaft\">OTCPK:BAYZF</a>) stock price continues to decline, and the stock has now dipped below \u20ac20 for the first time in more than 2 decades. <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712341-bayer-risks-remain-while-business-is-stabilizing\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4712341-bayer-risks-remain-while-business-is-stabilizing\" target=\"_blank\">In my last article</a>, I wrote that the risks</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1843440175/image_1843440175.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742535-bayer-stock-hits-two-decade-low-buy-again", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 11:08:22"}, {"id": "4742545", "title": "Culp, Inc. 2025 Q2 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Culp, Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q2 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106057\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742545-culp-inc-2025-q2-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:54:52"}, {"id": "4742532", "title": "SPY: Unconventional Economic Proxies Say More Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Lap point of view of man holding tablet\" data-id=\"466457490\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">triloks/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Preamble</strong></h2> <p>Over the years, it seems that government economic indicators have become less and less reliable. Take for instance <a href=\"https://www.shrm.org/mena/topics-tools/news/talent-acquisition/us-employment-gains-revised-down-over-800k-jobs#:~:text=Recent%20U.S.%20jobs%20gains%20weren,the%20BLS'%20annual%20data%20revision.\" rel=\"nofollow\">employment numbers</a>, in August, they were revised downwards by over 800,000, which is quite a sizeable adjustment, if you ask</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/466457490/image_466457490.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742532-spy-unconventional-economic-proxies-say-more-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 10:36:40"}]}